OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCOP26: UK firms forced to  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fshow how they will hit net 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fzero                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Most big UK firms and financial        
OL,6, institutions will be forced to show how
OL,7, they intend to hit climate change      
OL,8, targets, under proposed Treasury rules.
OL,10,FBy 2023, they will have to set out     
OL,11,Fdetailed public plans for how they will
OL,12,Fmove to a low-carbon future - in line  
OL,13,Fwith the UK's 2050 net-zero target.    
OL,15,FPlans will be submitted to an expert   
OL,16,Fpanel to ensure they are not just spin.
OL,18,FBut net-zero commitments will not be   
OL,19,Fmandatory and green groups say the     
OL,20,Fproposals do not go far enough.        
